org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan

Class ScanLiterals

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan.ScanLiterals

  • public class ScanLiterals
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of scan literals which provides various accessor methods which indicate the applicability of the scan literal collection under various scan operations. Given that a query may represent any number of scans or gets, clients should ensure that the collection is populated with literals applicable for its query expression context.
    Since:
    0.5
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
